{"tid":2295688,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Sony總裁回應《最後生還者2》爭議  指它是偉大的藝術","createTime":"2020-11-22T03:47:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-28T23:02:49.000Z","uid":67454,"like":3,"dislike":97,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e4776e8df6b456b18e71894c5497cc8db646e6ee","tid":2295688,"uid":67454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:47:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/jim-ryan-playstation-5-interview\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gq-magazine.co.uk%2Fculture%2Farticle%2Fjim-ryan-playstation-5-interview&d=yoW5vjLKqvFTs4XLOvP5rwV2WuQOZSh7uXaWrws9Zz8%3D&h=b74f202c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.gq-magazine.co.uk/culture/article/jim-ryan-playstation-5-interview</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n近日Sony總裁吉姆&middot;瑞恩接受了GQ-magazine的採訪，在訪談中他表示對PS5主機在未來7年的表現保持樂觀，還對《最後生還者2》受到的玩家差評進行了回應。<br />\n<br />\n對於 PlayStation Plus Collection 的遊戲陣容，他們還不確定是否要進行擴充。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">吉姆&middot;瑞恩:《最後生還者2》遊戲總監尼爾知道他創造了偉大的藝術。</span><br />\n<br />\n他知道自己已經成功地創造了以前從未在任何電子遊戲中以成熟方式解決的主題。<br />\n<br />\n我認為這是一件了不起的事情，而讓PlayStation成為發生這種情況的平台，我感到非常自豪。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我和尼爾都是大男孩了，我們不會讓自己被玩家帶來的阻力過分困擾。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">藝你老母術<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"50871f9ca7b8fe5fb9fccbe71f748904a61c61f0","tid":2295688,"uid":26773,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:51:35.000Z","msg":"眾人皆醉佢獨醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93f52cbd7b94b4830fd4deb7b479127ea8bbbfeb","tid":2295688,"uid":252784,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:52:15.000Z","msg":"Sony已經決定咗以後啲game要行咩路<br />\n第時大把屎等緊你地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d24bef0fbbebe1a1e8eef2805c0d32dce57d734","tid":2295688,"uid":34409,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-22T03:53:29.000Z","m